ZH: 中国是一个拥有完整主权和领土完整的国家。
EN: China is a country with complete sovereignty and territorial integrity.
ZH: 主权是国家在其领土范围内行使最高权力的能力。
EN: Sovereignty is the ability of a country to exercise supreme authority within its territorial borders.
ZH: 主权是国家自主决策和控制内外政治事务的基础。
EN: Sovereignty is the foundation for a nation to make autonomous decisions and control internal and external political affairs.
ZH: 主权是一种在国际关系中受到尊重和保护的重要概念。
EN: Sovereignty is an important concept that is respected and protected in international relations.
ZH: 每个国家都应该尊重其他国家的主权和独立。
EN: Every country should respect the sovereignty and independence of other nations.
ZH: 主权的原则是现代国际法的基石之一。
EN: The principle of sovereignty is one of the cornerstones of modern international law.
ZH: 主权国家有权利保护其国民免受外部干涉。
EN: Sovereign states have the right to protect their citizens from external interference.
ZH: 国际社会应该尊重每个国家的主权平等。
EN: The international community should respect the equal sovereignty of every nation.
ZH: 主权国家有责任维护自身的安全和独立。
EN: Sovereign states have the responsibility to safeguard their own security and independence.
ZH: 主权国家可以通过外交手段维护其国家利益。
EN: Sovereign states can defend their national interests through diplomatic means.
ZH: 军事干预违反了主权国家的自决权和国际法。
EN: Military intervention violates the right to self-determination and international law of sovereign states.
ZH: 任何人都不能侵犯国家的主权和领土完整。
EN: No one can violate a country's sovereignty and territorial integrity.
ZH: 他们争取主权的运动遭到了国际社会的广泛支持。
EN: Their movement for sovereignty has received widespread support from the international community. 
ZH: 主权不是绝对的，需要在国家的宪法和法律框架下行使。
EN: Sovereignty is not absolute and needs to be exercised within the constitutional and legal framework of a nation.
ZH: 此领土属于我国的主权范畴。
EN: This territory falls under the sovereignty of our country.
ZH: 这两个国家争执不下，主权问题一直是他们的争议点。
EN: The two countries have been in dispute, with the issue of sovereignty being their main point of contention. 
ZH: 这个地区的主权问题一直是国际政治的热点之一。
EN: The issue of sovereignty in this region has always been one of the hot topics in international politics.
ZH: 他们就该地区的主权问题进行了激烈的辩论。
EN: They engaged in intense debates over the issue of sovereignty in that region.
ZH: 主权转移是一种政治体制变革的重要形式。
EN: Transfer of sovereignty is an important form of political system transformation.
ZH: 他们通过谈判和协商解决了彼此之间的主权争端。
EN: They resolved their sovereignty dispute through negotiation and consultation.
